{"tid":181841,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"好攰好攰 每日起身返工都唔知為乜","createTime":"2017-04-01T01:47:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-01T16:45:15.000Z","uid":50727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"26725eec8d1897769a83583d894e3608e8403ff4","tid":181841,"uid":50727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T01:47:05.000Z","msg":"我真係好攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就黎頂唔黎喇好想喊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 每日一早起身返工都唔知為乜 公司仲要唔夠人要日日ot 人工又低一個人要做3個人嘅嘢 我大佬又要針對我 日日同班經理篤我背脊 但係我又乜都冇做過就屈9我<br />\n雖然我已經交左信 但都仲要捱多一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇人明我呢種感覺 有冇人可以安慰下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我呢個星期冇放過假 成身都好痛 好攰 好想一訓低就冇左件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce5b6d5c82c602194dbe9402479c18bcc948544f","tid":181841,"uid":40842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T01:54:43.000Z","msg":"巴打加油，不妨吹下水減壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做左幾年野? 講唔講得做邊行?"},{"pid":"d64bcf4191535f934f265366a90d4b51ed7c996d","tid":181841,"uid":7915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T01:55:38.000Z","msg":"交咗信大曬架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n公司唔夠人咪射佢波"},{"pid":"67dc621ed69388165ea776d393465f3f63a899ff","tid":181841,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T02:01:32.000Z","msg":"4,5 月有公眾假會好d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25cd252386586a6f0ec7289f5e503716794378d8","tid":181841,"uid":18257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T03:58:20.000Z","msg":"完全明<br />\n我依家日日都唔想起身返工 每個月得一兩日係準時返工<br />\n但放假就好會好早醒 因為覺得要把握每分每秒做啲令自己開心既事<br />\n平時返工 一返到公司 就開始唔舒服 一直反胃到中午<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw你加油 一個月好快過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40fd61b0727719b5b25ad65a96360ee15cc356de","tid":181841,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T06:50:08.000Z","msg":"遞咗信惡哂架喎<br />\nhea 做啦戇鳩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01bd3de315eda421afacefae0aba829927dab9ec","tid":181841,"uid":50727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T06:55:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>4,5 月有公眾假會好d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n飲食邊有得放公眾㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ecb162f9eb97f4a8e21eeb5435208b5d22cac3f","tid":181841,"uid":50727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T06:59:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打加油，不妨吹下水減壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做左幾年野? 講唔講得做邊行?</blockquote><br />\n做飲食 呢間做就做左唔係好耐 但問題係惡做 人手唔夠工時又長又冇得準時收工"},{"pid":"45f711d29ff5cdc527cce11d6108de2e6bc34e25","tid":181841,"uid":19867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T07:08:52.000Z","msg":"做飲食就預撚左辛苦嫁啦 人工又低"},{"pid":"b436ccab7e4b4289d19d7a158d78ad8bf9adb0c3","tid":181841,"uid":15140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T07:14:08.000Z","msg":"你講到咁 都仲未比人炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc7a01493701472dcf46259cd428742be8bde81f","tid":181841,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T07:14:45.000Z","msg":"為左儲錢供樓，養肥狗官，地產商，商家，新移民"},{"pid":"9aede72b575e384f14196d2e6bd9dbf468adc000","tid":181841,"uid":76747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T07:25:01.000Z","msg":"窮人出世係幫有錢人打工"},{"pid":"95f767b8c415f8b379d7439999a85fe4bd8709eb","tid":181841,"uid":50727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-0